<h1>World Sim Game Documentation Change Summary</h1>
<p>Version: Ver0.2.7</p>
<p>Baseline: Ver0.2.6.b.</p>
<p>Status: stabilization release metadata and implementation summary.</p>
<h2>Generated Official Files</h2>
<ul>
<li><code>docs/official/game_universal_documentation_ver0.2.7.doc</code></li>
<li><code>docs/official/versions/game_doc_ver0.2.7.doc</code></li>
<li><code>docs/official/versions/game_doc_ver0.2.7_change_summary.doc</code></li>
</ul>
<h2>Patch Delta</h2>
<ul>
<li>Updated the active version marker to <code>0.2.7</code>.</li>
<li>Added UID-backed per-civilization gameplay event history for country recent events.</li>
<li>Made right-side panel partial repainting atomic through an offscreen panel buffer.</li>
<li>Aligned world-generation progress stages and weights with the actual generation flow.</li>
<li>Adjusted map legend content by layer while preserving shallow/deep water terminology.</li>
<li>Changed normal-war truce duration to 55 years and severed/fallback truce duration to 25 years.</li>
<li>Kept collapse split truces at 45 years.</li>
<li>Added initial-truce duration data so diplomacy card bars scale correctly.</li>
<li>Cleaned remaining diplomacy-card mojibake strings touched by this release.</li>
</ul>
<h2>Validation</h2>
<ul>
<li><code>make check-text</code> required for release.</li>
<li><code>git diff --check</code> required for release.</li>
<li><code>make</code> required for release.</li>
<li>Executable smoke/probe checks required where available.</li>
</ul>
</body>
